      • addRangeValue

        public boolean addRangeValue(double dValue)
        填加分段专题图的分隔值
        参数:

        返回:
        添加成功返回true，否则返回false
        示例代码:
          Dataset dst = m_workspace.GetDataSourceAt(0).GetDatasetAt(2);
          ThemeRange themeRange = new ThemeRange();
          themeRange.setExpression("ID");
          Style style = new Style();
          style.lineColor = Color.RED;
          boolean bRt = themeRange.addRangeItem(style);
          bRt = themeRange.addRangeValue(2);
          style.lineColor = Color.BLUE;
          bRt = themeRange.addRangeItem(style);
          bRt = themeRange.addRangeValue(5);
          style.lineColor = Color.GREEN;
          bRt = themeRange.addRangeItem(style);
          bRt = themeRange.addRangeValue(7);
          style.lineColor = Color.YELLOW;
          bRt = themeRange.addRangeItem(style);
          bRt = themeRange.addRangeValue(10);
          int nCount = themeRange.getRangeItemCount();
          nCount = themeRange.getRangeValueCount();
          if (themeRange.isValid()) {
              m_mapView.AddThemeLayer(dst, themeRange);
          }
          m_mapView.Refresh();
